        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>A short cable assembly, with connectors is available from service parts to improve the electrical
                    connection to the heater switch (
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f9408091">Figure 1</hotlnk>). If either the switch or connector shows evidence of
                    looseness, both should be replaced.
                </para>
                <figure id="f9408091" figsize="pg-wide">
                    <graphic filename="../tsifigures/G9408091.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 1. Short Cable Assembly</caption>
                    <calloutgroup>
